	* oln/tests/arith/tests/min1: New test.
	* oln/tests/types/tests/bin2: New test.

	* oln/core/apply.hh: Add workaround for g++-2.95 ICE with
	direct meta class template parameter instanciation as function
	parameter.

	* oln/types/optraits_bin.hh: Add traits for min and max.

	* oln/morpho/minmax.hh: Remove useless min and max operators.
	Compatibility is preserved with older versions, but morpho::min
	and morpho::max for arithmetic operations are obsolete.

